title: Congratulations to HashiCorp! Enjoy the cake!
description: We’re thrilled to see our open source and tech partner HashiCorp join us in the public market. Public companies like HashiCorp, MongoDB, Confluent, and GitLab show that with the right business models, open source can be highly profitable. Here’s a look at HashiCorp’s history, our partnership, and a nod to the future.
